summary: https://www.patreon.com/monsterbonesart it’s launched! With the first set of content: an NPC character sheet for a water genasi...
caption:
https://www.patreon.com/monsterbonesart

it’s launched! With the first set of content: an NPC character sheet for a water genasi necromancer at level 2, and an accompanying character portrait! I’m aiming to get at least two character sheets out per week, and the accompanying character portraits being available at all tiers. 

There’s also the chance to request a custom character sheet, with or without accompanying character portrait! <3 

:V

for anyone who doesn’t wanna subscribe, because I get it, not everyone’s got money, a signal boost would be appreciated? Also I’m taking suggestions for other tiers, and have my regular stores still in effect!

Society 6

Redbubble!
